{"tid":2363651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多間美國企業因應衝擊國會事件暫停對共和黨捐款","createTime":"2021-01-12T11:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T20:44:37.000Z","uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1853e4c8cfcd49f3e40b1af679d67251d6f7481e","tid":2363651,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"在美國國會山莊衝擊事件後，愈來愈多商界企業表明，不會捐款給反對確認大選結果的共和黨人，這些企業包括阿馬遜、美國運通、Airbnb和Mastercard等。其中美國最大的賀卡製造商「賀曼卡片」 更表示，已經要求兩名共和黨參議員退還捐款。各間公司暫停捐款的年期不一，其中化工巨頭「陶氏化學」表示，會暫停向反對確認大選結果的國會議員捐款，直至他們的任期結束，部份最長可達6年。 報道指，今屆大選中，企業政治捐款達36億美元，是民主共和兩黨重要捐款來源。"},{"pid":"971f73e927d640c045a83a4e9043a93e84e37642","tid":2363651,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T19:46:39.000Z","msg":"有幾多gop人有反對確認先?<br />\n<br />\n佢o地會唔會寧願跪低?"},{"pid":"f6509683cdc6473123d0d598041320d97084384d","tid":2363651,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"呢招好撚絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b081a3d170e413584327880e5314ecfa246fb1","tid":2363651,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T19:51:41.000Z","msg":"deep state 上晒水 扮都唔扮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集團力量大到可以控制選舉 確保dem長期一黨專政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15e831a7a6b70d166563b520f83ca87c0cbdd55","tid":2363651,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T19:54:22.000Z","msg":"永續民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f758133332128fa748b969595a394c267b7134a","tid":2363651,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited